Calm down, calm down.

00:38:38.630 --> 00:38:40.290
I just want to tell you, Mr. Kondo,

00:38:41.750 --> 00:38:44.250
you don't need eyes to instantly

00:38:44.270 --> 00:38:45.770
tell two suits apart.

